http://www.myrecipes.com/recipe/artichoke-goat-cheese-spread
"3 ounces mild soft goat cheese, at room temperature","2  whole canned artichoke hearts, drained and finely chopped","2 tablespoons grated Parmesan","2  scallions, white and light green parts only, thinly sliced (about 1/4 cup)","1/2 teaspoon finely grated lemon zest","1 teaspoon lemon juice","1/4 teaspoon kosher salt","1/4 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper","  Pinch of red pepper flakes"